: "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L18,L21", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Los locks temporales (diario/semanal/mensual) ofrec\u00edan 'Desbloquear cuenta' pero la cuenta se re-bloqueaba al instante; se cambi\u00f3 el mensaje a 'se reactiva solo al renovarse el periodo' y el desbloqueo manual qued\u00f3 reservado para locks permanentes."}, {"id": "docs_changelog_ci_migrations", "label": "CI / migraciones (Supabase CLI, GitHub Actions)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L30-L35,L48-L49", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Node se fij\u00f3 a 20.12+ porque el toolchain no arranca con Node 18; la migraci\u00f3n advisor se hizo replay-safe porque user_ai_settings faltante romp\u00eda el db reset del CI; el nombre de la migraci\u00f3n add_color_theme_preferences se aline\u00f3 con la versi\u00f3n aplicada en prod para lograr un db push limpio."}, {"id": "docs_changelog_performance", "label": "Rendimiento (QueryClient, \u00edndices DB)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L26-L28", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "QueryClient refetcheaba todas las queries en cada navegaci\u00f3n; se fij\u00f3 staleTime 30s, se desactiv\u00f3 refetch-on-focus y retry se limit\u00f3 a 1. Se agreg\u00f3 \u00edndice trades(user_id, status, date desc) para acelerar dashboardStats."}, {"id": "docs_changelog_ai_resolve_provider", "label": "Motor de resoluci\u00f3n de IA (resolve-provider)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L45-L53", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "La causa ra\u00edz del error 'Configura ANTHROPIC_API_KEY' con OpenRouter configurado era que la capa de consumo IA le\u00eda provider/key solo de env vars, ignorando la config persistida en user_ai_configs; streamChat/embedText ahora reciben provider+apiKey expl\u00edcitos, y lib/ai/resolve-provider.ts centraliza el orden de resoluci\u00f3n (clave del usuario \u2192 env \u2192 none)."}, {"id": "docs_changelog_onboarding", "label": "Onboarding flow", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L22,L68", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_portfolio", "label": "Portfolio (curva de equity multi-cuenta)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L63", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_pwa", "label": "PWA (manifest, service worker, offline)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L66", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_pdf_export", "label": "Export PDF de reporte de rendimiento", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L67", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_formula_engine", "label": "Formula Engine", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L88", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_dashboardstats", "label": "dashboardStats (anal\u00edtica server-side)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": "L28,L89", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "docs_changelog_learning_system", "label": "Sistema de aprendizaje (repetici\u00f3n espaciada, streak)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", 